com.epoch.energyDiagrams

Class RCD

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.energyDiagrams.EDiagram
      • com.epoch.energyDiagrams.RCD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EDiagramConstants, EnergyQDatumConstants, RCDConstants

    public class RCD
extends EDiagram
implements RCDConstants
    A diagram correlating the energies of starting materials, intermediates, transition states, and products in a reaction. Consists of a table, each cell of which may contain one "state" (starting material, etc.).

        public final void setStates(String data)
                     throws ParameterException,
                            VerifyException
        Converts a string describing the locations, types, and labels of the diagrams' maxima and minima into array contents.
        Parameters:
        data - String in format 5=2=4/... where 5=2 represents the 1-based row and column and 4 represents a state labeled with label 4
        Throws:
        ParameterException - if the description of a cell is no good
        VerifyException - if the state of each cell cannot be calculated from its connections to other cells
